reviewText: Love TOFW.  Watch anytime I can for a spiritual boost.

I'm so grateful that these presentations are available for all of us woman that haven't been able to attend this event, and now have this source of inspiration available when ever we need it. I love having my friends over to my house, and being able to watch these as a sisterhood.  I wish that DVDs were available for each and every year they hold TOFW.
